\title{I've joined Coro}
\author{liamoc}
\date{2026-03-07}
\p{Last week I auditioned for [Coro](https://www.corocanberra.com/concerts), a festival concert choir located here in Canberra. I'm delighted to announce that they have invited me to sing with them starting with \em{Motets}, their first concert for 2026, scheduled in May. }